Why GL?
- Financial Statement, Audit, Central Bank ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßã‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ü‚Äî‡¶∏‡¶¨ ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá

