# üìä ‚ë¢ Trial Balance ‚Äî Accuracy Check

> Rule: Total Debit = Total Credit
---------------------------------------------
| Account         |      Debit |     Credit |
| --------------- | ---------: | ---------: |
| Cash            |     10,000 |          ‚Äî |
| Savings Deposit |          ‚Äî |     10,000 |
---------------------------------------------
| Total       | 10,000 | 10,000 |

‚úîÔ∏è Balanced ‚Üí Transaction Complete

