## üîÅ Ledger ‚Üí GL ‚Üí Trial Balance ‚Üí Balance Sheet


* Ledger: Detail ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶¨
* GL: Head-wise ‡¶Æ‡ßã‡¶ü
* Trial Balance: Debit = Credit ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶ï
* Balance Sheet: ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶•‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∂

